Good afternoon Charlie!  Sorry I am just now getting back to you.  I have been out of the office for a week sick and have been playing catch up ever since I have returned.  There is a few corrections that needs to be made that I and a few other department heads found.

From Becca: under the military and overseas voters put “to be announce, or you may contact our office at 606.679.2042”
Under the “register to vote or update registration tab under section “in person or at any of these agencies…. Should be WIC instead of WIG

content.text: Jenny called. She now does their editing on WordPress and she was having trouble getting it to accept her login. At first, she thought her password was not working so we changed it to "stanly2017". But, that did not work. She told me she was logging in by going to:
http://courthousecomputersystems.com/StanlyCountyROD/wp-admin
And, when she entered her login info it was giving her a message that the login was "not secure" (Just F.Y.I - this is the link I use to login so maybe it's only for me as a super admin?
Per User Manual that Shannon left, I instructed her to go to:
http://courthousecomputersystems.com/StanlyCountyROD/wp-login.php
This link prompted her for login and it worked this time. So, she book marked that link to use for future logins.
